The Owncloud server is client-based application that enables users to quickly find, manage, share and sync files through your Android or iOS devices. With advanced features like password protection, link expiration, anonymous and full access sharing, files are managed accordingly. Owncloud is designed to deliver via browser-interface to automatically upload pictures, sync files using the desktop client. It enables you to add third-party software with open and flexible architecture, ownCloud offers implementations of Dropbox, Microsoft OneDrive and many more. 
